PrecisONTARIO HYDRO NUCLEAR FACILITIES EXCLUSION FROM PART I OF THE CANADA LABOUR CODE REGULATIONS (INDUSTRIAL RELATIONS) which allow the Government of Ontario, through an agreement with the federal government, to administer and enforce provincial labour laws with respect to Ontario Hydro nuclear facilities employees, as of April 1, 1998.

ONTARIO HYDRO NUCLEAR FACILITIES EXCLUSION FROM PART I OF THE CANADA LABOUR
CODE REGULATIONS (INDUSTRIAL RELATIONS) which allow the Government of
Ontario, through an agreement with the federal government, to administer
and enforce provincial labour laws with respect to Ontario Hydro nuclear
facilities employees, as of April 1, 1998.
